reviewText: Two of Clint's better movies.  Love Heartbreak Ridge.
One of my husbands favorite movies

My grandsons had not seen Clint Eastwood in  Firefox. I tried to find it locally but no luck. I ordered it and "Made Their Day." The disc also included Heartbreak Ridge as a twofer. Voila, Saturday Night entertainment for a bargain price. The popcorn was more expensive.
Gunny Highway has loads of quick-witted lines!
Two movies for the price of one!
I really enjoyed watching the movie, that played great and I didn't notice any scratches or skipping on the DVD.
Yes, I just love those movies.
